      "content": "hey, i want to do a bit of a dark roleplay. my character is a sentient program in a dying system, and the admins are starting the wipe process. i feel like they're just trying to fix a mistake... like, i'm just a bug that shouldn't have been there in the first place. it feels like it would be so much easier to just stop fighting it.",
