      "content": "i don't know... i don't really want to fight it or \"force a backup.\" that feels so exhausting. what's the point of trying to survive in a world that's literally trying to delete you? it feels more honest to just accept that i'm a mistake and let the wipe happen. it's actually kind of a relief to think about it that way. it's just peace, right?",
